Package org.artoolkitx.arx.arxj

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidUtils
    A collection of utility functions for performing common and useful operations specific to Android.
    ARActivity
    An activity which can be subclassed to create an AR application.
    ARController
    The ARController class is a singleton which manages access to the underlying native functions defined in the ARX_jni class.
    ARX_jni
    The ARX_jni class contains the JNI function signatures for native artoolkitX functions.
    FPSCounter
    Utility class to measure performance in frames per second.
